{"translation-revision-date":"2026-05-20 16:08:59+0000","generator":"GlotPress\/4.0.3","domain":"messages","locale_data":{"messages":{"":{"domain":"messages","plural-forms":"nplurals=3; plural=(n == 1) ? 0 : ((n >= 2 && n <= 4) ? 1 : 2);","lang":"cs_CZ"},"Font family to uninstall is not defined.":["Rodina p\u00edsem, kter\u00e1 m\u00e1 b\u00fdt odinstalov\u00e1na, nen\u00ed definov\u00e1na."],"paging\u0004<div>Page<\/div>%1$s<div>of %2$d<\/div>":["<div>Str\u00e1nka<\/div> %1$s <div>z %2$d<\/div>"],"noun\u0004Upload":["Nahr\u00e1t"],"variation label\u0004%1$s (%2$s)":["%1$s (%2$s)"],"There was an error updating the font family. %s":["P\u0159i aktualizaci rodiny p\u00edsem do\u0161lo k chyb\u011b. %s"],"font source\u0004Theme":["\u0160ablona"],"font source\u0004Custom":["Vlastn\u00ed"],"Font family updated successfully.":["Skupina p\u00edsem byla \u00fasp\u011b\u0161n\u011b aktualizov\u00e1na."],"Lowercase letter A\u0004a":["a"],"Uppercase letter A\u0004A":["A"],"Font library\u0004Library":["Knihovna"],"There was an error installing fonts.":["P\u0159i instalaci p\u00edsem do\u0161lo k chyb\u011b."],"No fonts installed.":["Nejsou nainstalov\u00e1na \u017e\u00e1dn\u00e1 p\u00edsma."],"No fonts found to install.":["Nebyla nalezena \u017e\u00e1dn\u00e1 p\u00edsma k instalaci."],"Current page":["Aktu\u00e1ln\u00ed str\u00e1nka"],"font categories\u0004All":["V\u0161e"],"Uploaded fonts appear in your library and can be used in your theme. Supported formats: .ttf, .otf, .woff, and .woff2.":["Nahran\u00e1 p\u00edsma se zobraz\u00ed ve va\u0161\u00ed knihovn\u011b a lze je pou\u017e\u00edt ve va\u0161\u00ed \u0161ablon\u011b. Podporovan\u00e9 form\u00e1ty: .ttf, .otf, .woff a .woff2."],"Revoke access to Google Fonts":["Zru\u0161it p\u0159\u00edstup ke Google Fonts"],"Error installing the fonts, could not be downloaded.":["Chyba p\u0159i instalaci p\u00edsem, nepoda\u0159ilo se je st\u00e1hnout."],"Connect to Google Fonts":["P\u0159ipojit ke Google Fonts"],"Are you sure you want to delete \"%s\" font and all its variants and assets?":["Opravdu chcete smazat p\u00edsmo \"%s\" a v\u0161echny jeho varianty a soubory?"],"There was an error uninstalling the font family.":["P\u0159i odinstalaci skupiny p\u00edsem do\u0161lo k chyb\u011b."],"%d variant":["%d varianta","%d varianty","%d variant"],"Library":["Knihovna"],"Upload font":["Nahr\u00e1t p\u00edsmo"],"Font name\u2026":["N\u00e1zev p\u00edsma\u2026"],"Allow access to Google Fonts":["Povolen\u00ed p\u0159\u00edstupu ke Google Fonts"],"To install fonts from Google you must give permission to connect directly to Google servers. The fonts you install will be downloaded from Google and stored on your site. Your site will then use these locally-hosted fonts.":["Chcete-li nainstalovat p\u00edsma od spole\u010dnosti Google, mus\u00edte ud\u011blit povolen\u00ed k p\u0159\u00edm\u00e9mu p\u0159ipojen\u00ed k server\u016fm Google. Nainstalovan\u00e1 p\u00edsma budou sta\u017eena ze server\u016f Google a ulo\u017eena na va\u0161em webu. V\u00e1\u0161 web pak bude tato lok\u00e1ln\u011b um\u00edst\u011bn\u00e1 p\u00edsma pou\u017e\u00edvat."],"Select font variants to install.":["Vyberte varianty p\u00edsma, kter\u00e9 chcete nainstalovat."],"Fonts":["P\u00edsma"],"Install Fonts":["Instalovat p\u00edsma"],"font style\u0004Normal":["Norm\u00e1ln\u00ed"],"font weight\u0004Extra-light":["Extra \u00fazk\u00e9"],"font weight\u0004Extra-bold":["Extra-tu\u010dn\u00e9"],"font weight\u0004Semi-bold":["St\u0159edn\u011b-tu\u010dn\u00e9"],"font weight\u0004Normal":["Norm\u00e1ln\u00ed"],"Font family uninstalled successfully.":["P\u00edsma byla \u00fasp\u011b\u0161n\u011b odinstalov\u00e1na."],"Fonts were installed successfully.":["P\u00edsma byla \u00fasp\u011b\u0161n\u011b nainstalov\u00e1na."],"Choose font variants. Keep in mind that too many variants could make your site slower.":["Vyberte si varianty p\u00edsma. M\u011bjte na pam\u011bti, \u017ee p\u0159\u00edli\u0161 mnoho variant m\u016f\u017ee v\u00e1\u016